longBusinessSummary: Indeks Bilgisayar Sistemleri Mühendislik Sanayi ve Ticaret Anonim Sirketi distributes IT products in Turkey. The company's products portfolio includes computers/tablets, smartphones, printers, consumer electronics, software, peripherals, wearable technologies, data storage products, smart home products, and accessories. It purchases and sells spare parts and home electronics, as well as provides logistics and rental services. The company was incorporated in 1989 and is headquartered in Istanbul, Turkey.
